<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Help</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    {{>header}}
    <div class="main-content">
        
        <h1 class="main-title">Help</h1>
        <div class="weather-card">
            <p>
            Use this page to learn how to search for weather information and
            troubleshoot common issues.
            </p>
            <h2>How to Use the App</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Enter a city or location in the search box</li>
                <li>Select your preferred temperature unit</li>
                <li>Click “Search” to view the weather</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Common Issues</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Invalid location provided:</strong> "Unable to find location. Try another search." Make sure the search field has a valid address, no special characters.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Service unavailable:</strong> "Unable to connect to location services!" This may be a temporary connectivity issue. Try again later.
                </li>
            </ul>  
            <h2>Temperature Units</h2>
            <p>
                You can choose between Fahrenheit (°F) and Celsius (°C) using the
                dropdown next to the search field.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    {{>footer}}
</body>
</html>